validation_logic (S):
SELECT 
case when SEL_SEGMENT_IND IN ( 'E' , 'K' , 'L' , 'M' ,'N' , 'O' , 'P' , 'Q' ,'R' , 'T' , 'U' , 'V' ,'W' , 'B') then 'FORTITUDE' else 'AIG' END SEL_SEGMENT_IND
,sel_valdate
,case when sel_co in (10,19,22,25,48,52,56,72) OR sel_co < 10 OR sel_co > 72 then 'AGLA'
      when sel_co=31   then 'AAL'
      when sel_co=11   then 'AGL'
      when sel_co=33   then 'OLL'
      when sel_co in (12,32) then 'USL'
 else 'AGLA'  end company
,case when SEL_STATUS='2' then 'INACTIVE' else 'ACTIVE' end Status
,sum(SEL_UNITS) as units
,sum(W_MTERMVAL_END) as Mtermval_end 
,sum(SEL_POL_CNT) as Policy_count  
,sum(SEL_RDR_CNT) as Rider_count 
,sum(SEL_NO_CNT)  as Nocount 
FROM <#sourcetable#>
group by 
case when SEL_SEGMENT_IND IN ( 'E' , 'K' , 'L' , 'M' ,'N' , 'O' , 'P' , 'Q' ,'R' , 'T' , 'U' , 'V' ,'W' , 'B') then 'FORTITUDE' else 'AIG' END
,sel_valdate
,case when sel_co in (10,19,22,25,48,52,56,72) OR sel_co < 10 OR sel_co > 72 then 'AGLA'
      when sel_co=31   then 'AAL'
      when sel_co=11   then 'AGL'
      when sel_co=33   then 'OLL'
      when sel_co in (12,32) then 'USL'
  else 'AGLA'    end
,case when SEL_STATUS='2' then 'INACTIVE' else 'ACTIVE' end

validation_logic (S):
SELECT 
case when SEL_SEGMENT_IND IN ( 'E' , 'K' , 'L' , 'M' ,'N' , 'O' , 'P' , 'Q' ,'R' , 'T' , 'U' , 'V' ,'W' , 'B') then 'FORTITUDE' else 'AIG' END SEL_SEGMENT_IND
,sel_valdate
,case when sel_co in (10,19,22,25,48,52,56,72) OR sel_co < 10 OR sel_co > 72 then 'AGLA'
      when sel_co=31   then 'AAL'
      when sel_co=11   then 'AGL'
      when sel_co=33   then 'OLL'
      when sel_co in (12,32) then 'USL'
 else 'AGLA'  end company
,case when SEL_STATUS='2' then 'INACTIVE' else 'ACTIVE' end Status
,sum(SEL_UNITS) as units
,sum(W_MTERMVAL_END) as Mtermval_end 
,sum(SEL_POL_CNT) as Policy_count  
,sum(SEL_RDR_CNT) as Rider_count 
,sum(SEL_NO_CNT)  as Nocount 
FROM <#sourcetable#>
group by 
case when SEL_SEGMENT_IND IN ( 'E' , 'K' , 'L' , 'M' ,'N' , 'O' , 'P' , 'Q' ,'R' , 'T' , 'U' , 'V' ,'W' , 'B') then 'FORTITUDE' else 'AIG' END
,sel_valdate
,case when sel_co in (10,19,22,25,48,52,56,72) OR sel_co < 10 OR sel_co > 72 then 'AGLA'
      when sel_co=31   then 'AAL'
      when sel_co=11   then 'AGL'
      when sel_co=33   then 'OLL'
      when sel_co in (12,32) then 'USL'
  else 'AGLA'    end
,case when SEL_STATUS='2' then 'INACTIVE' else 'ACTIVE' end
